history.content:
At Girls Teaching Girls to Code (GTC), we empower college girls pursuing Computer Science and Engineering to connect with local high school girls and inspire them through mentorship and applied projects. Throughout the school year, we host events to extend the influence of women in technology and inspire young girls to pursue their interests in tech. We hope that you find the mission inspiring and invite you to join us in empowering womxn in tech! :) 

 

To learn more about GTC: https://www.girlsteachinggirlstocode.org/ 

 

**We are currently recruiting for new members **
Members Application (Due Sunday October 3rd, 10/03, at 11:59pm PST): https://tinyurl.com/gtcfall2021

If you have any questions feel free to email at samihamahin@berkeley.edu and joymaneetkaur@berkeley.edu
